OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'transform care'
OL,4,Cfor people with ME
OL,6,FIt comes after the high-profile death
OL,7,Fof a young woman from the disease.
OL,9,FMaeve Boothby-O'Neill, 27, suffered
OL,10,Fwith ME for a decade before she died
OL,11,Fat home in Exeter in October 2021 from
OL,12,Fsevere malnutrition.
OL,14,FHer inquest heard how she had been
OL,15,Fadmitted to the Royal Devon and Exeter
OL,16,FHospital three times that year for
OL,17,Ftreatment for malnutrition.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
