OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'transform care'
OL,4,Cfor people with ME
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, the Government said that
OL,7,Fit has created a plan which "outlines
OL,8,Fclear steps to improve care for
OL,9,Fpatients, by investing in research and
OL,10,Foffering access to care in the
OL,11,Fcommunity".
OL,13,FThe Department of Health and Social
OL,14,FCare (DHSC) acknowledged that many
OL,15,Fpeople with the condition "currently
OL,16,Fstruggle to access appropriate care
OL,17,Ftailored to their complex condition".
OL,19,FThe plan, which is expected to be
OL,20,Fpublished on Tuesday, will include new
OL,21,Ftraining for NHS workers, DHSC said.
