OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'transform care'
OL,4,Cfor people with ME
OL,6,FAnd the document will also include
OL,7,Ffunding for research, the DHSC said.
OL,9,FPublic health minister Ashley Dalton,
OL,10,Fsaid: "ME/CFS is a debilitating
OL,11,Fillness that can severely limit
OL,12,Fpatients' ability to participate in
OL,13,Feveryday activities, maintain
OL,14,Femployment, or enjoy family and social
OL,15,Flife.
OL,17,F"Today's plan will help tackle the
OL,18,Fstigma and lack of awareness of this
OL,19,Fcondition through improved training
OL,20,Ffor NHS staff.
OL,26,@rD@GOUyD@AOU
