OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'transform care'
OL,4,Cfor people with ME
OL,6,F"And through our neighbourhood health
OL,7,Fservices, we will ensure patients
OL,8,Fsuffering from the effects of ME/CFS
OL,9,Fcan access quality care, closer to
OL,10,Fhome, as pledged in our 10-Year Health
OL,11,FPlan.
OL,13,FBut Action for ME said that the plan
OL,14,F"does not go far enough".
OL,16,FSonya Chowdhury, chief executive of
OL,17,Fthe charity, said: "We appreciate the
OL,18,Ftime DHSC has put into the delivery
OL,19,Fplan and their engagement with us and
OL,20,Fthe ME community throughout.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUvD@XO]yD@TOU
