OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'transform care'
OL,4,Cfor people with ME
OL,6,F"However, the plan simply does not go
OL,7,Ffar enough. We are at the stage now
OL,8,Fwhere we need more than rhetoric, we
OL,9,Fneed to take a strategic approach if
OL,10,Fwe want a different outcome. What is
OL,11,Fproposed in the plan will not offer
OL,12,Fthis.
OL,14,F"We must have a funded, dedicated
OL,15,Fresearch hub to leverage our world-
OL,16,Fleading life sciences sector to unlock
OL,17,Ftreatments and ultimately cures for ME.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
