OL,3,CGovernment pledges to 'transform care'
OL,4,Cfor people with ME
OL,6,F"Without a commitment to better co-
OL,7,Fordinate research, people with ME will
OL,8,Fcontinue to be neglected, overlooked
OL,9,Fand, for many, confined to their homes.
OL,11,F"ME charities have been calling for
OL,12,Fthis funding to be accelerated for
OL,13,Fyears and we are still not seeing a
OL,14,Fstrategic approach to address this
OL,15,Fhistoric shortfall. Once again, it
OL,16,Ffeels like people with ME have been
OL,17,Fignored."
