OL,6,FDr Charles Shepherd, honorary medical
OL,7,Fadvisor and trustee at the ME
OL,8,FAssociation, said: "Whilst today's
OL,9,Fannouncement is an important step
OL,10,Fforward in helping to improve the
OL,11,Fquality of life of people with ME/CFS,
OL,12,Fthe Government must now go much
OL,13,Ffurther to improve their medical care
OL,14,Fand management and help to fund much
OL,15,Fneeded biomedical research into cause
OL,16,Fand treatment."
